<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="PN247-intro">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. avaḷ tīppāyvāḷaik kaṇṭu maturaipērālavāyār colliyatu. 
      ituvumatu – pūtappāṇṭiyaṉ ṟēvi peruṅkōppeṇṭū tīppāyavāḷaik kaṇṭu 
      <app>
      <lem wit="#C2 #C3 #C8">matuppōralavāmār</lem>
      <rdg wit="#C7">matu<gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="2"/>rālavāyār</rdg>
      </app>
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PN247">
<l>yāṉai tanta muḷimara viṟakiṟ</l>
<l>kāṉavar pottiya ñelitī viḷakkattu</l>
<l>maṭamāṉ perunirai vaikutuyi leṭuppi</l>
<l>manti cīkku maṇaṅkuṭai muṉṟili</l>
<l>ṉīrvār kūnta lirumpuṟan tāḻap</l>
<l>pērañar kaṇṇaḷ peruṅkāṭu nōkkit</l>
<l>terumaru mamma tāṉētaṉ koḻunaṉ</l>
<l>muḻavukaṇ ṭuyilāk kaṭiyuṭai viyaṉakarc</l>
<l>ciṟunaṉi tamiya ḷāyiṉu</l>
<l>miṉṉuyir naṭuṅkunta ṉiḷamaipuṟaṅ koṭuttē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="2">In [the light of] the lamp that is a fire rubbed by the forest people </l>
<l corresp="1">on firewood from a dry tree brought by an elephant, </l>
<l corresp="4">in the fearful front-yard scratched up by female monkeys, </l>
<l corresp="3">arousing from the sleep they stayed in a large herd of innocent deer, </l>
<l corresp="5">while [her] water-flowing tresses hang down [her] back, </l>
<l corresp="6">she whose eyes [hold] great grief looks at the great forest </l>
<l corresp="6a-c">[and] is unnerved, alas. </l>
<l corresp="9">Although she was very lonely, a little, </l>
<l corresp="7d-8">in the protected vast mansion of her husband where the eye of the drum does not sleep </l>
<l corresp="10">[her] precious life trembles when turning [her] back upon [her] youth. </l>
</lg>

    </div>
  </body>
</text>
